# Cursor Rules Mirroring

When `./_reference_ide-setup/` is present in the workspace and convention or rule changes are made in this project:

1. Map the change to the correct environment subfolder in the reference repo (Obsidian plugin → `obsidian-plugin/`, Android companion → `android-native/`).
2. Put cross-cutting changes in `shared/` only when they apply to all project types.
3. **Cursor is the sole supported AI instruction surface** — do not maintain `.github/copilot-instructions.md` or `.github/instructions/`.

See `_reference_ide-setup/.cursor/rules/reference-repo.mdc` for the full mirroring layout.
